            <td class="lds-col">Does not affirm the Nicene or Apostles' Creeds; views them as products of apostasy</td>
            <td class="main-col">Generally affirms the Nicene and Apostles' Creeds as foundational statements of faith</td>
          </tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
